videos.description: Juicy Landrum contests a shot, falls down and is able to lead the break off the miss for a lay-in on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Landrum’s defensive effort pays off with fast-break layup for Baylor) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Landrum's defensive effort pays off with fast-break layup for Baylor

videos.description: Juicy Landrum forces a steal, gets out in transition and threads the needle to Moon Ursin at the last moment for the layup.
